    "title": "Miujiza",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "miujiza",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Miujiza mara nyingi ilitokea katika Biblia. Ilikuwa ya kawaida hasa wakati wa Mose na huduma za Eliya, Elisha, Yesu, na mitume wake. Biblia haijaribu kuthibitisha miujiza; inaripoti tu. Miujiza inaonyesha nguvu za Mungu juu ya uumbaji na huruma yake kwa mahitaji ya binadamu.</p><p>Miujiza inaweza kuwafanya watu waamini katika Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:23\">Yohana 2:23</a>). Hata hivyo, imani ya kweli inahitaji zaidi ya kushuhudia muujiza pekee (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:37\">Yohana 12:37</a>). Miujiza inatukumbusha kwamba chochote kinawezekana kwa Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:21-Mark9:23\">Marko 9:21–23</a>; linganisha <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:26\">Mathayo 19:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:27\">Marko 10:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:37\">Luka 1:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:27\">18:27</a>).</p><p>Yesu alifanya miujiza mingi wakati wa huduma yake, ikiwa ni pamoja na kuponya wagonjwa, kufukuza pepo, kudhibiti asili, na kufufua wafu. Alionyesha upendo wa kina kwa watu kwa kukidhi mahitaji yao. Wengi walimfuata kwa sababu ya miujiza hii (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:2\">Yohana 6:2</a>). Hata hivyo, aliwaonya dhidi ya kumfuata tu kwa ajili ya miujiza (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:26\">Yohana 6:26</a>).</p><p>Miujiza mitatu mikuu inayohusishwa na Yesu ni:</p><ol><li><p>Kufika kwake kama &quot;Neno&quot; la Mungu katika mwili wa kibinadamu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:14\">Yohana 1:14</a>).</p></li><li><p>Kufufuka kwake kutoka kwa wafu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:1-Matt28:20\">Mathayo 28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:1-Mark16:8\">Marko 16:1–8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:1-Luke24:53\">Luka 24:1–53</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:1-John20:31\">Yohana 20:1–31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:3\">Matendo 1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:3-1Cor15:8\">1 Wakorintho 15:3–8</a>; tazama pia <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:6\">Matendo 23:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:8\">26:8</a>).</p></li><li><p>Mujiza wa kuzaliwa upya kiroho (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:3-John3:8\">Yohana 3:3–8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:20\">Wagalatia 2:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:8-Eph2:10\">Waefeso 2:8–10</a>).</p></li></ol><p>Yesu alikuja ulimwenguni ili kuokoa na kufa kwa ajili ya dhambi, akionyesha upendo mkuu wa Mungu kwa wanadamu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:16\">Yohana 3:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:8\">Warumi 5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:32\">8:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:4-Eph2:5\">Waefeso 2:4–5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:1-1John3:2\">1 Yohana 3:1–2</a>). Mungu kumfufua Yesu kutoka kwa wafu kunaonyesha nguvu zake juu ya kifo na kunatupa tumaini la uzima wa milele (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:3-1Pet1:9\">1 Petro 1:3–9</a>). Yeyote anayemwamini Yesu Kristo kama Mwokozi na Bwana amezaliwa upya kama mtoto wa Mungu na anapokea uzima wa milele (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:12\">Yohana 1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:36\">3:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:1-Rom5:2\">Warumi 5:1–2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:11-1John5:13\">1 Yohana 5:11–13</a>).</p><p>Kazi ya miujiza ya Yesu iliendelea kupitia wafuasi wake, kama inavyoonyeshwa katika kitabu cha Matendo (kwa mfano, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:1-Acts3:11\">Matendo 3:1–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:12-Acts5:15\">5:12–15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:8\">6:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:6-Acts8:7\">8:6–7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:32-Acts9:42\">9:32–42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:3\">14:3</a>). Wakiwa wamejazwa na Roho Mtakatifu, mitume na viongozi wengine wa Kikristo walifanya miujiza hii ili kuonyesha nguvu na ukweli wa ujumbe wa Kikristo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:3\">14:3</a>; tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:2\">Yohana 3:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:4\">Waebrania 2:4</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:23-Matt19:26\">Mathayo 19:23–26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:1-Matt28:20\">28:1–20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:23-Mark10:27\">Marko 10:23–27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:30-Luke1:38\">Luka 1:30–38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:24-Luke18:27\">18:24–27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:1-Luke24:53\">24:1–53</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:12-John1:14\">Yohana 1:12–14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:2-John3:8\">3:2–8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:16\">16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:1-John21:25\">20:1–21:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:29-Acts4:31\">Matendo 4:29–31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:12-Acts5:16\">5:12–16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:8\">6:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:4-Acts8:23\">8:4–23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:32-Acts9:42\">9:32–42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:3-Acts14:4\">14:3–4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:8\">26:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:1\">Warumi 5:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:8\">8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:32\">8:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:4-Eph2:5\">Waefeso 2:4–5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:8-Eph2:10\">8–10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:4\">Waebrania 2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:3-1Pet1:5\">1 Petro 1:3–5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:12-1John5:13\">1 Yohana 5:12–13</a></p>",
